ary":"Lorsque Robert lll de Stuteville est né environ 1075, à Estouteville, Normandie, France, son père, Robert ll d'Estouteville, avait 37 ans et sa mère, Beatrix of Valmont, avait 32 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils et 2 filles. Il est décédé en 1140, à Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, France, à l’âge de 66 ans."},"de":{"about 1075–1140":"um 1075–1140","1075–1140":"1075–1140","1088–Male":"1088–Verstorben","1091–Male":"1091–Verstorben","1100–1172":"1100–1172","1112–Female":"1112–Verstorben","–1191":"–1191","1040–1107":"1040–1107","1045–Female":"1045–Verstorben","1091":"1091","1385":"1385","1088":"1088","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","1040":"1040","1172":"1172","1191":"1191","1107":"1107","1112":"1112","1045":"1045","1100":"1100","about 1075":"um 1075","Cottingham, East Riding Yorkshire, England":"England","Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Upper Normandy, France":"Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, Frankreich","Estouteville, Normandy, France":"Estouteville, Normandie, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Als Robert lll de Stuteville um 1075 in Estouteville, Normandie, Frankreich geboren wurde, war sein Vater Robert ll d'Estouteville 37 und seine Mutter Beatrix of Valmont 32. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn und 2 Töchter. Er starb 1140 im Alter von 66 Jahren in Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, Frankreich."},"ht":{"about 1075–1140":"about 1075–1140","1075–1140":"1075–1140","1088–Male":"1088–Desede","1091–Male":"1091–Desede","1100–1172":"1100–1172","1112–Female":"1112–Desede","–1191":"–1191","1040–1107":"1040–1107","1045–Female":"1045–Desede","1091":"1091","1385":"1385","1088":"1088","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","1040":"1040","1172":"1172","1191":"1191","1107":"1107","1112":"1112","1045":"1045","1100":"1100","about 1075":"about 1075","Cottingham, East Riding Yorkshire, England":"England","Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Upper Normandy, France":"Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, France","Estouteville, Normandy, France":"Estouteville, Normandie, France"},"hu":{"about 1075–114